The paper deals with machine learning and classification tasks, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper specifically focuses on rare class recognition and emerging novel subclasses, which are relevant to all of these sub-categories. However, given that the paper deals with both text and image data, cs.CV and cs.CL may be slightly less likely than the others.
